type: TS Trading Session Error - Invalid Label Property Value

definition.text: This property expects you to define the Time Frame in which the Trading Session is going to run. The current value assigned to the property is not recognized as a valid value.

paragraphs.text: The value you currently have is invalid. You need to change it and run the Trading Session again.
The property at the moment has the following value. Note that a value will be shown below only if you received this error, not when you navigate to this error page via other means.
